reviewText: NICE CANDYE KANE 1 SCENE, {The other scenes were of old vhs videos} BUT THE REST WAS VINTAGE BLURRY STUFF, YEAH IT HAD MY OTHER FAVORITE CRISTY CANYON BUT IT WAS TAME, IT WAS A COPY OF OTHER STUFF PUT TOGETHER ON A COMPUTER, IT COULD HAVE BEEN BETTER IF HE USED AN HD COPIER INSTEAD OF THIS.
